<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَاصِرَاتُ الطَّرْفِ}</span> ... قَصَرْنَ أَبْصَارَهُنَّ عَلَى أَزْوَاجِهِنَّ؛ فَلَا يَنْظُرْنَ إِلَى غَيْرِهِمْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٥٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَطْمِثْهُنَّ}</span> ... يَطَاهُنَّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٦٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمِن دُونِهِمَا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> أَدْنَى مِنَ الجَنَّتَيْنِ السَّابِقَتَيْنِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُدْهَامَّتَانِ}</span> ... خَضْرَاوَانِ قَدِ اشْتَدَّتْ خُضْرَتُهُمَا حَتَّى مَالَتْ إِلَى السَّوَادِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٦٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَضَّاخَتَانِ}</span> ... فَوَّارَتَانِ بِالمَاءِ؛ لَا تَنْقَطِعَانِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَيْرَاتٌ}</span> ... زَوْجَاتٌ طَيِّبَاتُ الأَخْلَاقِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حُورٌ}</span> ... نِسَاءٌ بِيضٌ حِسَانٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٧٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَّقْصُورَاتٌ}</span> ... مَسْتُورَاتٌ مَصُونَاتٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَطْمِثْهُنَّ}</span> ... يَطَاهُنَّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَفْرَفٍ خُضْرٍ}</span> ... وَسَائِدَ ذَوَاتِ أَغْطِيَةٍ خُضْرٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٧٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَعَبْقَرِيٍّ}</span> ... فُرُشٍ، وَبُسُطٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٧٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَبَارَكَ}</span> ... كَثُرَتْ بَرَكَتُهُ، وَخَيْرُهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>